{"tid":1398364,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解會無人提罷市架？？？？","createTime":"2019-08-02T18:43:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T18:47:11.000Z","uid":109433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bc23e2be1009785ae40c95736c6a98e7ac45d218","tid":1398364,"uid":109433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T18:43:09.000Z","msg":"多人都淨係記得三罷要罷工<br />\n無人宣傳過罷市 （罷學就收皮 個個放緊summer)<br />\n甚至有人個態度係想繼續幫襯無罷既食肆<br />\n<br />\n大佬 唔返工都要食飯架！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n傻啦<br />\n點解商戶有生意唔做要罷市？<br />\n除左佢地本身既政治取態之外<br />\n更重要既係開左門都無生意做 <br />\n會蝕燈油火蠟人工 所以先會無奈罷市<br />\n呢種型式既罷市先係最重要既<br />\n因為呢種舖頭先會由旁觀者心態轉移成受害人心態<br />\n先會向政府施壓呀<br />\n有生意做洗乜要罷市呀on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔該 罷得一日就專業啲啦<br />\n一早買定自己煮 去集會食乾糧食一日都得掛？<br />\n比啲骨氣啦香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地衣加係要拉越黎越多人陪我地攬炒做受害人啊<br />\n最好日日罷 罷到無得再冷處理我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49a7f723f64e5a5ed2e007c27bc87cdb5a61af0d","tid":1398364,"uid":109433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T18:44:36.000Z","msg":"黑警仆街係要追究<br />\n但唔好唔記得我地係對制度無能而憤怒<br />\n黑警只係反映制度無能既事實黎！！！<br />\n記得做事要治本<br />\nreset hong kong先係最有效既方法！！"},{"pid":"0f8e97cdb1fb46c48f1f0e7481827bc75eb4b198","tid":1398364,"uid":109433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T18:44:52.000Z","msg":"reset hong kong!"},{"pid":"7f04752cb6778d10c1a7c4b4330c022a2002807b","tid":1398364,"uid":109433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T18:45:03.000Z","msg":"reset hong kong!"},{"pid":"f2f860c0532b3482f88ca60b1851cfa12a85ebd4","tid":1398364,"uid":109433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T18:45:13.000Z","msg":"reset hong kong!"},{"pid":"386df6169f0cda5195eb30b44f490ebd3fb0e5e1","tid":1398364,"uid"